{"tid":1203414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多位連登仔可唔可以幫吓我呢個垃圾00後","createTime":"2019-06-11T12:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:00:20.000Z","uid":256205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab52612148600fcf9234411ba05f5263a928f53","tid":1203414,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"唔理你今晩11點，12號清晨出都好，幫手解答吓我嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n事源學校係紅底軍校，入面嘅綿羊似乎都冇人組織罷課，小弟我要12號即係聽日放學先去到做back up，我明白最關鍵係早上，但我就係比垃圾又無謂嘅責任感拖撚住，我相信咁多位義士烈日當空去年晏就都仲需要有人做back up，警犬日光日白都唔會咁張揚，但封路搜身呢啲一地走唔甩。想問下如果到時要中途加入有邊啲位可以入，仲有可以幫到咩手。<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家，呢幾日tg都有啲亂，仲係有啲唔清晰，如果我有咩講錯大力啲屌我就得。"},{"pid":"4ce8fcc80a25dfd1d06af8a55c9555da274da35a","tid":1203414,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"90de88dde3c9c4dc74c581b48b59563fe9464edc","tid":1203414,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:56:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bff881d52fad4e77b743d33b34e851136d488a64","tid":1203414,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:56:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"862816de1b171679f66117be931fe44c14511cb7","tid":1203414,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dd6cc7b12dfedf6fd8a7a21ac844dbb9fd540d54","tid":1203414,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:59:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4aa8bc08aa03952b9fcc90c76565aea854f8dec","tid":1203414,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11beba5c51677c787162420f5efd7229fb758e57","tid":1203414,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:00:20.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}